{"tid":89701,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［第六轉生］［1Q題］小豬，小牛，小雞同小狗一齊去踢波","createTime":"2017-01-21T13:55:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-26T13:44:22.000Z","uid":27396,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"93aa0bcd1106c71bac8e7ce99874359d009f1221","tid":89701,"uid":27396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T13:55:32.000Z","msg":"小豬，小牛，小雞同小狗一齊去踢波，佢地平時會沖埋涼加飲水抖陣先至返去學校，今日佢哋球場戰況十分激烈，踢左太耐，最後只好跑返學校，但係又驚比老師發現，小狗係呢個時候就提出左行學校後樓梯返上去，大家都同意，最後係行上去果時有一隻小動物死都唔行上去，係邊隻動物，同埋點解？<br />\n<br />\n呢次轉生諗起以前係高登睇到一個post嘅標題而諗到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n不過應該唔會咁快估到<em><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </em><br />\n照舊第五頁開估，第三頁可以問我拎提示，但我未必會答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f31fe745ba42a284d33f89f84c076ae9fa8432e","tid":89701,"uid":8655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T13:56:32.000Z","msg":"牛唔飲水唔行得"},{"pid":"dcf7c74c847a5b2faecda3d0f24dafe5edf61520","tid":89701,"uid":13835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T13:56:36.000Z","msg":"象<br />\n因為蟻多嬲死象"},{"pid":"1499f87d7842629dc5356d560518da5f24ea04f9","tid":89701,"uid":13835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T13:57:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>牛唔飲水唔行得</blockquote><br />\n屌你老母"},{"pid":"dfeb295692741d404da39572157bd8d737f457d7","tid":89701,"uid":20119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T13:57:11.000Z","msg":"馬死落地行"},{"pid":"8af3396221b7bc33fd26ce487c8686c6178216e5","tid":89701,"uid":35173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T13:57:54.000Z","msg":"屎急馬行田"},{"pid":"935d0760f67351a5745325a465d769a507d8fba6","tid":89701,"uid":8655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T13:58:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>牛唔飲水唔行得</blockquote><br />\n屌你老母</blockquote><br />\n第三個回覆可以問我拎提示"},{"pid":"8f093c239f97801618986e87467af7f